  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/e648b875e3f03aebe40baa32c01766c1.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/e648b875e3f03aebe40baa32c01766c1.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice, the reaper girl, found herself lost in the Underworld! She must escape this forgotten land before the corruption takes over everything, but she's not alone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of a Soulblaster, a weapon capable of shooting souls, and her new friends, Alice will face the dangers and become, once and for all, a Soulslinger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2ae9b9338b4a23cece4055055f69ec55.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2ae9b9338b4a23cece4055055f69ec55.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reaping an enemy soul will recover your Soulvolver ammo!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroying obstacles and defeating enemies helps the level progression; the more you destroy, the faster you'll progress! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blessings and curses are permanent power ups, each one with it's own special effect!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pies are consumable temporary power ups, each one with it's own purpose; use them wisely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2082fca0d0a7f4bed5600e4749c3ad70.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2082fca0d0a7f4bed5600e4749c3ad70.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three levels of difficulty;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five stages, each one with its own boss;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three special Soulblasters to use; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nineteen different blessings to obtain;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five flavors of pies;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five playable characters skins;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ hats to collect;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/0043a08f78d15a170e40d0fdad581057.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/0043a08f78d15a170e40d0fdad581057.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keyboard:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD or Arrow Keys - Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Mouse Button - Attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold left mouse button for autoswing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right Mouse Button - Switch weapon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift or Space - Use pie</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >P or Esc - Pause</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter - Confirm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F4 - Toggle fullscreen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Stick or Direction Pad - Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A, X, Shoulders or Triggers - Attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right Stick - Move cursor, aim and switch weapon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B or Y - Use pie</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start - Pause</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A - Confirm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Back - Open Steam Friends</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/e648b875e3f03aebe40baa32c01766c1.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/e648b875e3f03aebe40baa32c01766c1.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice, the reaper girl, found herself lost in the Underworld! She must escape this forgotten land before the corruption takes over everything, but she's not alone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of a Soulblaster, a weapon capable of shooting souls, and her new friends, Alice will face the dangers and become, once and for all, a Soulslinger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2ae9b9338b4a23cece4055055f69ec55.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2ae9b9338b4a23cece4055055f69ec55.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reaping an enemy soul will recover your Soulvolver ammo!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroying obstacles and defeating enemies helps the level progression; the more you destroy, the faster you'll progress! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blessings and curses are permanent power ups, each one with it's own special effect!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pies are consumable temporary power ups, each one with it's own purpose; use them wisely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2082fca0d0a7f4bed5600e4749c3ad70.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/2082fca0d0a7f4bed5600e4749c3ad70.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three levels of difficulty;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five stages, each one with its own boss;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three special Soulblasters to use; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nineteen different blessings to obtain;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five flavors of pies;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five playable characters skins;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ hats to collect;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/0043a08f78d15a170e40d0fdad581057.apng?t=1774143540\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154570/extras/0043a08f78d15a170e40d0fdad581057.poster.avif?t=1774143540\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keyboard:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD or Arrow Keys - Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Mouse Button - Attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold left mouse button for autoswing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right Mouse Button - Switch weapon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift or Space - Use pie</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >P or Esc - Pause</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter - Confirm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F4 - Toggle fullscreen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Stick or Direction Pad - Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A, X, Shoulders or Triggers - Attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right Stick - Move cursor, aim and switch weapon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B or Y - Use pie</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start - Pause</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A - Confirm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Back - Open Steam Friends</p></li></ul>",
